      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/22/2/10/80",
      "text": [
        ": سمعت أبا عبد الله يقول: إنْ بلغَكم عن صاحبكم غيبةٌ فلا تنكروها."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.abdullah-al-shahin": [
          "(42) Muhammad bin Ya’qoob narrated from some of his companions from Ahmad bin Muhammad from Ali bin al-Hakam from Abu Ayyoob al-Khazzaz from Muhammad bin Muslim that Abu Abdullah as-Sadiq (as) had said: “If you are informed that your man has disappeared, do not deny that.” The same was narrated by Muhammad bin Ya’qoob from Ali bin Ibraheem bin Hashim from Muhammad bin Abu Omayr from Abu Ayyoob al-Khazzaz from Muhammad bin Muslim."
        ]
      }
